***************************
New functionality required:
***************************

1. Enable coma asymmetry. Required changes will include the ability to specify n angular (conical) regions with unique outflow velocity and production rate. CVODE will therefore need to be called n times, and the resulting populations from each run need to be assigned to the relevant grid cells (within each respective predefined conical region), before raytracing. In the first instance, 2 conical regions will be sufficient.